    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid, reliable option for daily commuting. While it shows some expected signs of wear, such as minor exterior scuffs and some interior aging, it has been mechanically maintained and starts reliably every time. It\u2019s a practical choice for anyone looking for a functional car that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
