    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a dependable daily driver for several years. While the engine and transmission remain functional, the car does show its age with some minor fluid leaks and a less refined idle. Visually, there are noticeable scratches on the exterior and some staining on the interior upholstery. It is a solid option for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections and basic maintenance needs.",
